{"snp4.15:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.15 ","snp4.15:0.2":"Attadandasutta ","snp4.15:1.1":"“Attadanda bhayam jatam, ","snp4.15:1.2":"janam passatha medhagam; ","snp4.15:1.3":"Samvegam kittayissami, ","snp4.15:1.4":"yatha samvijitam maya. ","snp4.15:2.1":"Phandamanam pajam disva, ","snp4.15:2.2":"macche appodake yatha; ","snp4.15:2.3":"Annamannehi byaruddhe, ","snp4.15:2.4":"disva mam bhayamavisi. ","snp4.15:3.1":"Samantamasaro loko, ","snp4.15:3.2":"disa sabba samerita; ","snp4.15:3.3":"Iccham bhavanamattano, ","snp4.15:3.4":"naddasasim anositam. ","snp4.15:4.1":"Osane tveva byaruddhe, ","snp4.15:4.2":"Disva me arati ahu; ","snp4.15:4.3":"Athettha sallamaddakkhim, ","snp4.15:4.4":"Duddasam hadayanissitam. ","snp4.15:5.1":"Yena sallena otinno, ","snp4.15:5.2":"disa sabba vidhavati; ","snp4.15:5.3":"Tameva sallamabbuyha, ","snp4.15:5.4":"na dhavati na sidati. ","snp4.15:6.1":"Tattha sikkhanugiyanti, ","snp4.15:6.2":"yani loke gadhitani; ","snp4.15:6.3":"Na tesu pasuto siya, ","snp4.15:6.4":"nibbijjha sabbaso kame; ","snp4.15:6.5":"Sikkhe nibbanamattano. ","snp4.15:7.1":"Sacco siya appagabbho, ","snp4.15:7.2":"amayo rittapesuno; ","snp4.15:7.3":"Akkodhano lobhapapam, ","snp4.15:7.4":"veviccham vitare muni. ","snp4.15:8.1":"Niddam tandim sahe thinam, ","snp4.15:8.2":"pamadena na samvase; ","snp4.15:8.3":"Atimane na tittheyya, ","snp4.15:8.4":"nibbanamanaso naro. ","snp4.15:9.1":"Mosavajje na niyetha, ","snp4.15:9.2":"rupe sneham na kubbaye; ","snp4.15:9.3":"Mananca parijaneyya, ","snp4.15:9.4":"sahasa virato care. ","snp4.15:10.1":"Puranam nabhinandeyya, ","snp4.15:10.2":"Nave khantim na kubbaye; ","snp4.15:10.3":"Hiyyamane na soceyya, ","snp4.15:10.4":"Akasam na sito siya. ","snp4.15:11.1":"Gedham brumi mahoghoti, ","snp4.15:11.2":"Ajavam brumi jappanam; ","snp4.15:11.3":"Arammanam pakappanam, ","snp4.15:11.4":"Kamapanko duraccayo. ","snp4.15:12.1":"Sacca avokkamma muni, ","snp4.15:12.2":"Thale titthati brahmano; ","snp4.15:12.3":"Sabbam so patinissajja, ","snp4.15:12.4":"Sa ve santoti vuccati. ","snp4.15:13.1":"Sa ve vidva sa vedagu, ","snp4.15:13.2":"Natva dhammam anissito; ","snp4.15:13.3":"Samma so loke iriyano, ","snp4.15:13.4":"Na pihetidha kassaci. ","snp4.15:14.1":"Yodha kame accatari, ","snp4.15:14.2":"Sangam loke duraccayam; ","snp4.15:14.3":"Na so socati najjheti, ","snp4.15:14.4":"Chinnasoto abandhano. ","snp4.15:15.1":"Yam pubbe tam visosehi, ","snp4.15:15.2":"Paccha te mahu kincanam; ","snp4.15:15.3":"Majjhe ce no gahessasi, ","snp4.15:15.4":"Upasanto carissasi. ","snp4.15:16.1":"Sabbaso namarupasmim, ","snp4.15:16.2":"Yassa natthi mamayitam; ","snp4.15:16.3":"Asata ca na socati, ","snp4.15:16.4":"Sa ve loke na jiyati. ","snp4.15:17.1":"Yassa natthi idam meti, ","snp4.15:17.2":"Paresam vapi kincanam; ","snp4.15:17.3":"Mamattam so asamvindam, ","snp4.15:17.4":"Natthi meti na socati. ","snp4.15:18.1":"Anitthuri ananugiddho, ","snp4.15:18.2":"Anejo sabbadhi samo; ","snp4.15:18.3":"Tamanisamsam pabrumi, ","snp4.15:18.4":"Pucchito avikampinam. ","snp4.15:19.1":"Anejassa vijanato, ","snp4.15:19.2":"Natthi kaci nisankhati; ","snp4.15:19.3":"Virato so viyarabbha, ","snp4.15:19.4":"Khemam passati sabbadhi. ","snp4.15:20.1":"Na samesu na omesu, ","snp4.15:20.2":"Na ussesu vadate muni; ","snp4.15:20.3":"Santo so vitamaccharo, ","snp4.15:20.4":"Nadeti na nirassati”ti. ","snp4.15:20.5":"Attadandasuttam pannarasamam. "}